Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.49,0:10:13.42,BirdyD,Loudspeaker,0,0,0,,{\be1\3c&H4B8D3C&\pos(344,89)}Kagami Shouko na vás bude čakať,\N v prednej časti výťahu na 6. poschodí.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.42,0:10:14.82,BirdyD,Loudspeaker,0,0,0,,{\be1\3c&H4B8D3C&\pos(350,48)}Opakujem.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.74,0:10:17.70,BirdyD,Loudspeaker,0,0,0,,{\be1\3c&H4B8D3C&\pos(336,51)}Slečna Arita Shion.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.53,0:10:37.04,BirdyD,Fanboy,0,0,0,,{\be1}Je to naozaj skutočná Shiorin!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.04,0:10:39.66,BirdyD,Fanboy,0,0,0,,{\be1}To dievča proste nie je len návnada.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.52,0:10:41.99,BirdyD,Shouko,0,0,0,,{\be1}To je Arita Shion!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.99,0:10:44.58,BirdyD,Shouko,0,0,0,,{\be1}Idol Arita Shion je tu!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.47,0:10:52.28,BirdyD,Fanboy,0,0,0,,{\be1}Tadiaľ!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.10,0:10:57.94,BirdyD,Guy,0,0,0,,{\be1}Sú nákupy s týmto hotové?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.94,0:11:00.00,BirdyD,Hayamiya,0,0,0,,{\be1}Ďakujem, si veľká pomoc.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.00,0:11:02.00,BirdyD,Fanboy,0,0,0,,{\be1}Tu je! \NTo je Shiorin!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.00,0:11:03.64,BirdyD,Fanboy,0,0,0,,{\be1}Podpíš sa mi, prosím!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.64,0:11:05.48,BirdyD,Hayamiya,0,0,0,,{\be1}Čo je to tu za rozruch?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.48,0:11:08.42,BirdyD,Guy,0,0,0,,{\be1}Neviem. \NMožno je tu nejaký umelec.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.42,0:11:09.60,BirdyD,Hayamiya,0,0,0,,{\be1}V žiadnom prípade.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.72,0:11:13.19,BirdyD,Fanboy,0,0,0,,{\be1}Podpíšte sa , prosím!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.19,0:11:14.72,BirdyD,Fanboy,0,0,0,,{\be1}Prosím, povedzte hlášku.{Kulag: I have no idea what else to put, since we've been leaving it out the whole time.}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.13,0:11:16.89,BirdyD,Fanboy,0,0,0,,{\be1}Kúpil som si CD!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.89,0:11:18.61,BirdyD,Fanboy,0,0,0,,{\be1}Fotku!\N Stačí chvíľka!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.61,0:11:21.03,BirdyD,Birdy,0,0,0,,{\be1}To prekliate decko.
