Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.71,0:11:43.05,BirdyD,Shouko,0,0,0,,{\be1}Ty si tak hlúpy idol.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.72,0:11:46.01,BirdyD,Fanboy,0,0,0,,{\be1}Arita Shion naozaj prišla!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.01,0:11:47.54,BirdyD,fanboy,0,0,0,,{\be1}Videl som obrázok textovej správy.{TLC: When people text others with a picture attached}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.54,0:11:48.96,BirdyD,fabnoy,0,0,0,,{\be1}Nie je to návnada!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.41,0:11:53.84,BirdyD,Birdy,0,0,0,,{\be1}To nemá odvahu sa mi postaviť!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.35,0:11:56.19,BirdyD,Tsutomu,0,0,0,,{\be1}Je to dieťa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.19,0:11:57.47,BirdyD,Birdy,0,0,0,,{\be1}Nezáleží na tom!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.47,0:11:59.00,BirdyD,Birdy,0,0,0,,{\be1}Ak chce boj, potom ho bude mať.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.00,0:12:00.66,BirdyD,Tsutomu,0,0,0,,{\be1}Je na rovnakej úrovni.
